south
#
@desc
You slowly walk south towards the old Courthouse and Police Department.  The large buildings to your 

left are crumbling, causing random pieces of large concrete to fall on to the sidewalk you are walking

on.  One of the largest buildings you can see hase a large, blackened hole in the middle of it though

the fire had long burnt out. In the early days of the infection, the military responded with the full

force of their armorment.  This is likely a display of that force, what little it did.  You can see some

figures huddled around a trashcan fire. Down the road you can see the path to the left that leads to the

remanants of the old Courthouse.
